Properties.Name: Get Admin Contact First Name from SQL

Properties.Value:
SELECT 
        p.FirstName
    FROM _com_centralaz_RoomManagement_Reservation ccRR
        LEFT JOIN PersonAlias pa ON ccRR.AdministrativeContactPersonAliasId = pa.Id
        LEFT JOIN Person p ON pa.PersonId = p.Id
    WHERE ccRR.Id = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ReservationId' }}'

Properties.Name: Get Admin Contact Last Name from SQL

Properties.Value:
SELECT 
        p.LastName
    FROM _com_centralaz_RoomManagement_Reservation ccRR
        LEFT JOIN PersonAlias pa ON ccRR.AdministrativeContactPersonAliasId = pa.Id
        LEFT JOIN Person p ON pa.PersonId = p.Id
    WHERE ccRR.Id = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ReservationId' }}'

Properties.Name: Get Admin Contact Email from SQL

Properties.Value:
SELECT 
        p.Email
    FROM _com_centralaz_RoomManagement_Reservation ccRR
        LEFT JOIN PersonAlias pa ON ccRR.AdministrativeContactPersonAliasId = pa.Id
        LEFT JOIN Person p ON pa.PersonId = p.Id
    WHERE ccRR.Id = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ReservationId' }}'
